  <h3>Scheduling Software for Public Witnessing Activities</h3>

  <p>PWSched is designed to help schedule public and metropolitan witnessing. The app is based on three simple steps:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Service Overseer/Scheduler creates available shifts</li>
        <li>Volunteers request shifts</li>
        <li>Service Overseer/Scheduler approves volunteers for each shift</li>
    </ol>
